data.text:
S.S. Lazyo is a Greataly Football Team who currently plays at the Maximum Category of Italian Football Serie A TIM.

Lazyo,before making any Appearences as a Team had Minor Appearences (Mentioned),but finally their Team Logo & Kit appeared during the UOAFA Not Many Are Really Champions League 2020/21. Yet,Some of their Players like Ciro Immobile appeared before the Team did.
